title: Shania Twain - The Specials [2001] DVD5
description: Shania Twain - The Specials [2001] DVD5 Canadian pop diva Shania Twain is shown here in the lead role in two incredibly successful television projects. The first project, the WINTER BREAK, was filmed in Miami and Ontario and was broadcast on CBS in March 1999. He includes live performances, including the participation of Backstreet Boys and Elton John, and also shows Twain's life from within through interviews with family and friends. The second project, COME ON OVER, which aired in November 1999, contains another concert performance with behind-the-scenes footage, where special guests - Troy Aikman and Dallas Cowboys cheerleaders take part.
